Flowmaster's Force II cat-back exhaust system for the 2011-2015 GM 2500HD/3500HD extended cab/short bed truck is perfect for the person looking for mild to moderate sound levels with all of the performance benefits that you would expect from Flowmaster.  This bolt-on emissions-legal system for the 6.0L V8 (gas) engines features a 50 Series Big Block muffler, mandrel bent 3.50" stainless steel tubing, and a polished 4.00" stainless steel tip with Flowmaster's logo embossed into it.  The exhaust system is manufactured in the USA and is covered by Flowmaster's Lifetime Limited Warranty.  Designed for an easy fit, this system includes all necessary parts and hardware for installation.
